  "detailed_description": "<h1>Refreshing Car Wash!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/be5692fc6f5609cf0b596144c0417b29.avif?t=1772361534\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Car Wash is a cozy experience where you transform dirty, old cars into gleaming masterpieces. Enjoy the relaxing process of scrubbing, polishing, and adding the perfect finishing touch with the power of fresh soap and a hint of clean perfume!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/c90f62f4727377edbd3cd8c83e5b9ba0.poster.avif?t=1772361534\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/c90f62f4727377edbd3cd8c83e5b9ba0.webm?t=1772361534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/c90f62f4727377edbd3cd8c83e5b9ba0.mp4?t=1772361534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Car Wash</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Car Wash, dive into a relaxing and satisfying experience where you bring life back to dirty, neglected cars. Use tools like sponges, air blowers, and polishers to scrub away grime, polish surfaces, and make every vehicle shine like new.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/dc8b370c0b05871530e472bea1e98db5.poster.avif?t=1772361534\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/dc8b370c0b05871530e472bea1e98db5.webm?t=1772361534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/dc8b370c0b05871530e472bea1e98db5.mp4?t=1772361534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the soothing process of cleaning and restoring, with the fresh scent of soap and a touch of clean perfume to complete each masterpiece. Whether it’s removing stubborn stains or adding the perfect shine, Car Wash lets you embrace the joy of making old cars sparkle again.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Car Wash is a cozy experience where you transform dirty, old cars into gleaming masterpieces. Enjoy the relaxing process of scrubbing, polishing, and adding the perfect finishing touch with the power of fresh soap and a hint of clean perfume!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/c90f62f4727377edbd3cd8c83e5b9ba0.poster.avif?t=1772361534\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/c90f62f4727377edbd3cd8c83e5b9ba0.webm?t=1772361534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/c90f62f4727377edbd3cd8c83e5b9ba0.mp4?t=1772361534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Car Wash</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Car Wash, dive into a relaxing and satisfying experience where you bring life back to dirty, neglected cars. Use tools like sponges, air blowers, and polishers to scrub away grime, polish surfaces, and make every vehicle shine like new.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/dc8b370c0b05871530e472bea1e98db5.poster.avif?t=1772361534\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/dc8b370c0b05871530e472bea1e98db5.webm?t=1772361534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372510/extras/dc8b370c0b05871530e472bea1e98db5.mp4?t=1772361534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the soothing process of cleaning and restoring, with the fresh scent of soap and a touch of clean perfume to complete each masterpiece. Whether it’s removing stubborn stains or adding the perfect shine, Car Wash lets you embrace the joy of making old cars sparkle again.</p>",
